<li sourcefile="ProcessDoku/02_SupportProcesses/02_01_Finance/localizations/rus-tax-agent.md" sourcestartlinenumber="70"><p sourcefile="ProcessDoku/02_SupportProcesses/02_01_Finance/localizations/rus-tax-agent.md" sourcestartlinenumber="70">In the <strong sourcefile="ProcessDoku/02_SupportProcesses/02_01_Finance/localizations/rus-tax-agent.md" sourcestartlinenumber="70">Value</strong> field, enter the VAT percentage.</p>
</li>
<li sourcefile="ProcessDoku/02_SupportProcesses/02_01_Finance/localizations/rus-tax-agent.md" sourcestartlinenumber="71"><p sourcefile="ProcessDoku/02_SupportProcesses/02_01_Finance/localizations/rus-tax-agent.md" sourcestartlinenumber="71">Close the page.</p>
