<li sourcefile="ProcessDoku/02_SupportProcesses/02_01_Finance/localizations/rus-tax-agent.md" sourcestartlinenumber="73"><p sourcefile="ProcessDoku/02_SupportProcesses/02_01_Finance/localizations/rus-tax-agent.md" sourcestartlinenumber="73">Create a sales tax group, and enter the required information.</p>
