<h2 id="create-a-vendor-that-your-company-acts-as-a-tax-agent-for-and-post-transactions" sourcefile="ProcessDoku/02_SupportProcesses/02_01_Finance/localizations/rus-tax-agent.md" sourcestartlinenumber="92">Create a vendor that your company acts as a tax agent for, and post transactions</h2>
<p sourcefile="ProcessDoku/02_SupportProcesses/02_01_Finance/localizations/rus-tax-agent.md" sourcestartlinenumber="94">On the <strong sourcefile="ProcessDoku/02_SupportProcesses/02_01_Finance/localizations/rus-tax-agent.md" sourcestartlinenumber="94">Vendors</strong> page, you can define a vendor as a tax agent. You can then perform transactions with this vendor.</p>
