</li>
<li sourcefile="ProcessDoku/02_SupportProcesses/02_01_Finance/localizations/rus-tax-agent.md" sourcestartlinenumber="99"><p sourcefile="ProcessDoku/02_SupportProcesses/02_01_Finance/localizations/rus-tax-agent.md" sourcestartlinenumber="99">In the <strong sourcefile="ProcessDoku/02_SupportProcesses/02_01_Finance/localizations/rus-tax-agent.md" sourcestartlinenumber="99">Vendor type</strong> field, select the type of vendor:</p>
